Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道现在几点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天早晨都这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我又来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我来帮藤本先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鸠 藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要帮忙的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君一定轻松了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 为什么我非得让人帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 一定不要大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看藤本君这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个没盯好他又要蛮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的

