Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天一天地...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我找到了这个 贴在这里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别擅自...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...小鸠的愿望.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天去了图书馆 前天去了大学里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说兼职已经请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过多少次了 同情...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同情也不是好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了你很烦人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生有出去散步过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步很好 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有趣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只有你觉得而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他们两个一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要时间呢 不管对谁来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你们两个一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生的这里 总是皱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想让藤本先生能开心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有小船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生一起去坐小船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那些小船...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(出租小船)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像得花钱...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀咧呀咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 藤本先生伤还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你这样划 就永远回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会加油的 会加油划的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让船桨进到水里太深
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把脚也用上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 船动了 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够悠闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里稍微好一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 想让藤本先生恢复些精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来一起去给鱼先生喂吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是问你这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道现在是什么情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 又让藤本先生花钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次我拿回零钱了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不是问你这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 所以我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我的话还没说完 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼先生 吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生也试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人呆会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是跟着的话 我静不下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去收集几个金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 这不是琥珀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在散步吗 今天天气确实很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不紧不慢的气氛怎么这么强烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是不紧不慢的 帮我说说这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说小鸠小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 把自己的愿望都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃晃悠悠不紧不慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 土鸠那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是个土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生气吗 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到她的那样的表情...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐已经做出了选择了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的事情都是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 没有任何一件事是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指天界里吗 对异界的人也适用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适用于所有的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你总抓着我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是指...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得到我的感谢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可找错门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你并没有什么感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来也不会有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为藤本先生是我重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在意重要的人是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管风琴 现在由清花老师保管着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于藤本先生来说 那是件重要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想弹的话随时可以去弹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得藤本先生和五百祗先生很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如总是很生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗 是你一直带在身边的布偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其实是个很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做出了选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你怎么洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾洗好的衣服很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不能陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是再好不过了 终于能解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生能感到高兴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 是这样啊 很仓促呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢平日的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也想和千帆和千世打个招呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们一定会感到寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对清花说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算去说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠来到我家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个季节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天也好 夏天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天也好 冬天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个季节都过得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安顿下来的话 记得联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 安顿下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把金平糖集满的话你就...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己会怎样已经无所谓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傻瓜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百分满分的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打好招呼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀咧呀咧 他还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 月亮很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不做只是陪伴在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会感到痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能仅仅陪伴在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是件非常难得的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠可能是说不出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有说去哪了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只说安顿下来就会联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是有点傻有点笨有点缺根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了开朗和直率毫无可取之处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为一个人已经算是很好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的灵魂真的已经算很好的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求求你 让她消失这件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她消失这件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 兔子先生很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要道歉 这是我自己决定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在开玩笑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后还让你生气了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不说就走掉了 你是什么意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我说的话让你不开心了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是契约啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里啊 这里 箱子上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...布偶...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是装成布偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说契约对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什么意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂之冠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的小鸠的灵魂是不属于任何一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不代表任何生命的暧昧存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根据和某位高权重人士的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了可以重生一次 重新生活的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠放弃了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了在剩下的时间里 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以契约被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 必须消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在藤本先生的身边真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没用呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来最后想笑着告别的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生是...我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖...满了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠的愿望改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是契约是不能改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想去的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生的...金平糖...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就像是诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 让小鸠转生到这个世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别道歉 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她在一起时间最长的我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 发生的事全部都是必然的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要去我该去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[明天到来的日子...]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}なくしたものと あつめたものの狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所失与所得的缝隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの笑顔　落ちていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遗落着你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}届きそうで　届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}仿佛伸手可及却又遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}飛んでゆけるわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飞又飞不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}笑わせてあげたいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我只是想让你有更多笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}役立たずのこの翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这没用的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}何のためにあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}到底为什么存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの傍で笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我会在你身边微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私に出来ること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这是我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}暖めるだけでもいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕给你一丝为暖也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}せめて包みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}至少想包容着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}気付くの　そのための翼と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}终于发觉 双翼是为此存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}今こそわたし　笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所以我现在 在微笑
